rows.label: qst711002_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! This is wonderful!
It looks perfect!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0002
rows.name: Well then, without further ado...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0003
rows.name: Th-this is...?!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0004
rows.name:
Meat and fish simmered in a sweet
broth that whets the appetite...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0005
rows.name: Wh-what a delicious dish!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0006
rows.name: ...But!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0007
rows.name:
This is not a dish from
my hometown, Chilsain!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0008
rows.name: Because...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0009
rows.name: ...it's delicious!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0010
rows.name:
The food my mother made didn't
have such a refined taste...!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0011
rows.name:
The broth smelled of fish,
and the meat was dry and
tough. It was despairing!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0012
rows.name:
That kind of junk food taste
is Superbian cuisine!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0013
rows.name:
I wish someone could recreate
that nostalgic taste...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0014
rows.name:
But I doubt a decent person could
do it, and maybe you have to be
from Superbia to understand...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0015
rows.name:
*Sigh*... I want to eat that
nostalgic Chilsainian Kascha...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0016
rows.name:
The reason it was delicious was
probably because the person who
made it had miraculous skills.

rows.label: qst711002_msg0017
rows.name:
...So, please use this
recipe next time!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0018
rows.name:
With this recipe, I'm sure we can
create a junk food-like and original
Superbian dish this time!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0019
rows.name: Well then, I'm counting on you!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0101
rows.name:
I wish someone could recreate
that nostalgic taste...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0102
rows.name:
*Sigh*... I want to eat that
nostalgic Chilsainian Kascha...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0201
rows.name:
Ah, everyone! How is it? Is
the Superbian dish ready?

rows.label: qst711002_msg0202
rows.name: Th-this is?!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0203
rows.name:
Wh-what should I say... It looks
like it could destroy every last
bit of a person's appetite...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0204
rows.name:
W-well, looks aren't everything in
cooking. So, if you'll excuse me...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0205
rows.name: Ugh?!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0206
rows.name: U-uuuuuuuuugh...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0207
rows.name: ...It's awful!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0208
rows.name: This is it! This is the taste!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0209
rows.name:
A violently stimulating spice
that makes it impossible to
tell what you're eating!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0210
rows.name:
The crunchy texture of dahl that's
been simmered until it's bone dry!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0211
rows.name:
This horribly seasoned dish that's
almost an insult to call cooking is
the true essence of Superbian cuisine!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0212
rows.name:
Well, I said it was junk
food and rough, but...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0213
rows.name:
In my hometown, there was no one
other than my mother who could
make such awful Superbian food.

rows.label: qst711002_msg0214
rows.name:
Huh? Miss Blade over there,
why are you looking at me
with such murderous eyes?

rows.label: qst711002_msg0215
rows.name: Still, thank you all so much!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0216
rows.name:
If you ever visit Superbia,
please come to my family's home!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0217
rows.name:
Next time, I'll treat you to some
authentic Superbian cuisine! Hahaha!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0301
rows.name:
Understand? Delicious Superbian food
cannot be called Superbian food!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0302
rows.name:
A junk food-like and original
taste! That is the taste
of home I remember!
